<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="6" color="#000066">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="4" color="#ff6600"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="6" color="#c0c0c0"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><span lang="en-GB"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;">The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our attention which may affect your children.</div><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;">I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of chickenpox in a pupil in one of our Year 5 classes. Chickenpox is a contagious and mild virus which is extremely common amongst young children. It causes a rash of red, itchy spots that turn into blisters and eventually fall off. Symptoms usually go away without treatment, but because the infection is very contagious, an infected child should stay home and rest until the symptoms are gone. If your child exhibits symptoms, please keep them away from school, let us know and seek appropriate medical attention.</div><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;">Please click for further information about <a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/chickenpox/Pages/Introduction.aspx">chickenpox&nbsp;</a></div><br><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Warm Regards,</span></font></font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="color: rgb(80, 0, 80); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Mrs. Alison Mackey</span><br style="color: rgb(80, 0, 80); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(80, 0, 80); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Deputy Head of Primary</span></font></div></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><br></p></div></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">____